{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917430/extras/feltolt2.png?t=1737238714\" /><br><strong>Action-packed, dynamic tower defense where mana management, strategic spellcasting and quick decisions are crucial. Know your enemies, defeat them with your deadliest spell build and become a master of magic!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNLEASH YOUR ULTIMATE POWER</strong></h2>Running low on mana? No problem! Along with spells, you have access to a range of helpful abilities that you can unlock and upgrade as you progress through the story.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917430/extras/g01.gif?t=1737238714\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SET UP THE BEST SPELL BUILD</strong></h2>No mission is impossible, you can pick the right spell combinations for every battle. The variety of enemies ensures that you need to adapt your tactics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917430/extras/g02.gif?t=1737238714\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>USE THE POWER OF THE ELEMENTS</strong></h2>Got some fire mages giving you trouble? Alright, turn them into ice cubes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917430/extras/g03.gif?t=1737238714\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PREPARE FOR CHALLENGING BOSS FIGHTS</strong></h2>Numerous boss fights await you on your journey. With leveling, learning, and patience, even the most formidable foes will fall before you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917430/extras/g04.gif?t=1737238714\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIGHT YOUR WAY ACROSS THE WORLD</strong></h2><i>The world of Aarnhagor is under grave threat. Influenced by an unknown force, the inhabitants of the world have turned against their own kind 